00:32:17,470 --> 00:32:18,740
like you?

521
00:32:21,380 --> 00:32:22,380
Cha Eun Sang.

522
00:32:23,950 --> 00:32:24,980
Did I...

523
00:32:26,750 --> 00:32:28,150
miss you?

524
00:32:50,009 --> 00:32:53,579
(Jeguk High School)

525
00:32:57,609 --> 00:33:00,049
- I told you to leave.
