everyone to leave?

532
00:33:19,640 --> 00:33:21,900
I had to find something out
from Upstart.

533
00:33:23,509 --> 00:33:24,710
Don't be nervous.

534
00:33:30,950 --> 00:33:33,049
- What are you doing?
- What are you doing?

535
00:33:33,819 --> 00:33:35,079
You have come at a good time.

536
00:33:41,319 --> 00:33:43,059
