537
00:33:46,059 --> 00:33:47,160
Can you see this?

538
00:34:00,609 --> 00:34:01,680
Take a look.

539
00:34:02,710 --> 00:34:04,579
You never spent money
for real before.

540
00:34:06,079 --> 00:34:07,349
You're not an upstart, are you?

541
00:34:11,989 --> 00:34:12,989
Lee Bo Na.

542
00:34:15,159 --> 00:34:16,730
Is she really an upstart?

543
00:34:20,699 --> 00:34:22,530
I heard that you know
a little about her.

544
00:34:22,530 --> 00:34:26,000
I don't know. You're so childish.
What does that matter to you?

545
00:34:26,139 --> 00:34:27,199
It matters to me.

546
00:34:28,139 --> 00:34:31,510
If she pretended to be an upstart
when she's on a welfare scholarship,

547
00:34:32,309 --> 00:34:35,110
