551
00:34:50,130 --> 00:34:52,300
Will it be too rude to ask you...

552
00:34:53,159 --> 00:34:54,530
what makes you so cheeky?

553
00:34:57,800 --> 00:34:58,840
Step aside.

554
00:35:00,699 --> 00:35:01,900
Bo Na, what's wrong?

555
00:35:03,769 --> 00:35:04,809
What happened?

556
00:35:04,869 --> 00:35:07,039
Chan Young, Choi Young Do
finally went crazy.

557
00:35:12,780 --> 00:35:14,880
You keep disturbing everyone
preparing for class.

558
00:35:15,820 --> 00:35:17,289
You're starting to annoy me.

559
00:35:20,760 --> 00:35:23,630
