568
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:23,650
This is big news.

569
00:36:23,789 --> 00:36:26,360
Choi Young Do turned the Upstart's
bag inside out next door...

570
00:36:26,360 --> 00:36:27,690
asking if she's really an upstart.

571
00:36:27,690 --> 00:36:29,489
- When?
- Just now.

572
00:36:29,489 --> 00:36:31,760
He was quiet for a few days,
and now he's starting again.

573
00:36:32,130 --> 00:36:33,599
All right, everyone.

574
00:36:33,760 --> 00:36:37,230
Take your seats, please.
