583
00:37:42,869 --> 00:37:44,300
(Complaint)

584
00:37:44,300 --> 00:37:45,639
(Accuser, Choi Young Do)

585
00:37:45,639 --> 00:37:47,340
(The accuser sues the accused
for assault, so please punish him.)

586
00:37:50,070 --> 00:37:53,179
Please drop the charge.

587
00:37:53,239 --> 00:37:57,579
Come on. Don't give in so easily.
You're disappointing me.

588
00:37:57,949 --> 00:38:00,349
Did you hit me without
even thinking through this much?

589
00:38:02,050 --> 00:38:04,289
How nice did you think I was?

590
00:38:12,500 --> 00:38:13,500
Please.

591
00:38:13,960 --> 00:38:15,699
I got three weeks of
medical treatment.

592
00:38:15,829 --> 00:38:17,170
I was in so much pain.

593
00:38:17,469 --> 00:38:20,300
Tears were pouring
because I was so sad.

594
00:38:21,869 --> 00:38:22,940
I'm sorry.

595
00:38:24,269 --> 00:38:27,139
Please drop the charge. Please...

596
00:38:27,480 --> 00:38:30,650
How could I do that when I was hit?

597
00:38:32,480 --> 00:38:33,619
So my friend,

598
00:38:35,449 --> 00:38:39,889
take this back and spend a lot
of money to get a good lawyer.

599
00:38:41,989 --> 00:38:43,329
I'll do anything you want.

600
00:38:45,190 --> 00:38:47,059
You're making me get soft-hearted.

601
00:38:50,099 --> 00:38:53,739
Then... I can't guarantee you
that it will work,

602
00:38:54,539 --> 00:38:56,070
but will you go on your knees?

603
00:39:03,179 --> 00:39:05,150
Who knows? My mind might change.

604
00:39:08,019 --> 00:39:10,989
(Complaint)

605
00:39:57,869 --> 00:39:59,900
Hey, stand up.

606
00:40:01,639 --> 00:40:03,210
It's none of your business.

607
00:40:03,210 --> 00:40:05,309
- Stand up.
- Don't pretend to be nice.

608
00:40:05,840 --> 00:40:07,079
Because you are not.

609
00:40:07,880 --> 00:40:09,880
You're no different
from Choi Young Do.

610
00:40:11,409 --> 00:40:14,550
As I expected,
our Joon Young is so smart.

611
00:40:15,750 --> 00:40:16,750
By any chance,

612
00:40:18,650 --> 00:40:20,289
