613
00:40:20,289 --> 00:40:23,730
Choi Young Do at least
remembered it.

614
00:40:25,730 --> 00:40:26,800
I'm sorry.

615
00:40:27,800 --> 00:40:30,730
I'll repay you like this instead.

616
00:40:40,010 --> 00:40:43,880
I also hit you, so you should
make me go on my knees too.

617
00:40:47,519 --> 00:40:48,550
Can I do that?

618
00:40:48,719 --> 00:40:49,719
I'm looking forward to it.

619
00:40:49,719 --> 00:40:50,820
How would I be feeling then?

620
00:40:58,059 --> 00:41:00,800
What are you doing?
Who is fighting?

621
00:41:03,630 --> 00:41:05,000
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

622
00:41:10,570 --> 00:41:11,710
What are you doing?

623
00:41:17,679 --> 00:41:21,019
Don't you have to go
to the hospital? Doesn't it hurt?

624
00:41:21,619 --> 00:41:23,690
This could happen between friends,

625
00:41:24,820 --> 00:41:26,360
but my heart is so broken.

626
00:41:27,590 --> 00:41:28,989
I'm so sorry.

627
00:41:29,789 --> 00:41:31,659
Your father will be upset
if he sees this.

628
00:41:31,659 --> 00:41:33,500
I won't sue him, so don't worry.

629
00:41:36,099 --> 00:41:37,300
That's not what I meant.

630
00:41:37,969 --> 00:41:40,199
I'm apologizing as Tan's mother
right now.

631
00:41:41,340 --> 00:41:43,909
You've just transferred here,
and you're already causing trouble?

632
00:41:44,340 --> 00:41:45,880
Did you have to do this
as soon as you came?

633
00:41:46,480 --> 00:41:48,610
Have you forgotten
about the promise we made?

634
00:41:49,849 --> 00:41:50,849
I'm sorry.

635
00:41:50,849 --> 00:41:52,550
If you're going to be like this,
transfer to another school.

636
00:41:53,019 --> 00:41:54,480
I warned you,
and you made a promise.

637
00:41:54,480 --> 00:41:56,119
What more should I do about you?

638
00:41:56,550 --> 00:41:58,519
Who should I tell this
to make you scared?

639
00:41:59,019 --> 00:42:00,289
Should I tell your brother?

640
00:42:01,489 --> 00:42:02,860
I'm okay, ma'am.

641
00:42:03,360 --> 00:42:05,190
Don't be too harsh on Tan.

642
00:42:18,039 --> 00:42:19,940
Your mother also recommended it.

643
00:42:24,780 --> 00:42:26,280
You should consider transferring.

644
00:42:29,050 --> 00:42:31,849
Wouldn't it be right for the person
embarrassed from getting hit to go?

645
00:42:31,849 --> 00:42:34,190
Are you disregarding her
since she's not your real mother?

646
00:42:40,300 --> 00:42:41,329
Just go...

647
00:42:42,260 --> 00:42:43,869
before your right side
also gets beaten.

648
00:42:43,869 --> 00:42:45,030
I'm waiting for that.

649
00:42:46,500 --> 00:42:48,940
The chance that I don't have
to hold back anymore.

650
00:42:50,570 --> 00:42:51,739
Do you want to hit me once more?

651
00:42:53,610 --> 00:42:55,340
I think there will be
another chance.

652
00:43:09,860 --> 00:43:12,800
(Kim Tan)

653
00:43:16,000 --> 00:43:19,369
(Choi Young Do)

654
00:43:21,940 --> 00:43:23,010
Choi Young Do.

655
00:43:25,980 --> 00:43:27,139
Why are you avoiding me?

656
00:43:27,139 --> 00:43:28,480
I'm not avoiding you.

657
00:43:28,480 --> 00:43:30,280
Is it because the thing
we saw the other day?

658
00:43:30,949 --> 00:43:32,179
Because you're embarrassed?

659
00:43:34,380 --> 00:43:35,650
What about the other day?

660
00:43:36,420 --> 00:43:37,690
What did we see?

661
00:43:37,690 --> 00:43:38,690
Choi Young Do.

662
00:43:40,019 --> 00:43:41,659
That's not embarrassing.

663
00:43:42,590 --> 00:43:43,730
It's just hurtful.

664
00:43:43,730 --> 00:43:44,860
What do you know?

665
00:43:44,929 --> 00:43:46,659
Everyone has a secret like that.

666
00:43:47,630 --> 00:43:48,860
It's also the same for me.

667
00:43:50,530 --> 00:43:51,530
To tell you the truth,

668
00:43:53,070 --> 00:43:54,469
I'm not the chief director's son.

669
00:43:56,309 --> 00:43:57,510
What?

670
00:43:57,510 --> 00:43:58,940
My real mom is a different person.

671
00:44:00,710 --> 00:44:03,579
You're the first person
I'm telling about this.

672
00:44:03,579 --> 00:44:04,909
Are you the son of a mistress?

673
00:44:07,750 --> 00:44:08,750
So...

674
00:44:09,849 --> 00:44:13,159
if a child is born between my dad
and the woman we saw yesterday...

675
00:44:13,420 --> 00:44:14,989
You're just like the child,
aren't you?

676
00:44:42,179 --> 00:44:43,820
I heard that Tan beat Young Do up.

677
00:44:43,949 --> 00:44:46,019
What a pity. I didn't see that.

678
00:44:46,019 --> 00:44:48,489
You should say it properly.
Young Do wasn't hit, he blocked Tan.

679
00:44:48,489 --> 00:44:51,690
Why don't you just say that
Young Do's jaw hit Tan's fist?

680
00:44:51,690 --> 00:44:53,230
You should stop hanging around
with Young Do.

681
00:44:53,230 --> 00:44:54,829
You really won't be able to go
to college later.

682
00:44:54,829 --> 00:44:57,030
You should hate the crime
within legal boundaries.

683
00:44:57,030 --> 00:44:58,230
You shouldn't hate the person.

684
00:44:58,230 --> 00:44:59,940
Isn't Young Do the victim this time?

685
00:44:59,940 --> 00:45:01,400
Are you taking
Choi Young Do's side...

686
00:45:01,400 --> 00:45:02,739
after I suffered like that?

687
00:45:02,739 --> 00:45:04,170
You're subtly taking Kim Tan's side.

688
00:45:04,170 --> 00:45:05,309
Old affection is scary.

689
00:45:05,309 --> 00:45:08,179
I don't have any old affection
toward Kim Tan.

690
00:45:08,409 --> 00:45:10,550
- Be quiet.
- Who cares if she hears it?

691
00:45:10,610 --> 00:45:12,750
Do we have to walk on eggshells
around Kim Tan's fiancee?

692
00:45:12,849 --> 00:45:13,949
Hey, Yoo Rachel.

693
00:45:16,750 --> 00:45:17,889
Do you have something to say?

694
00:45:17,889 --> 00:45:18,949
Don't you have anything to say?

695
00:45:19,219 --> 00:45:20,559
You should go first. I'll catch up.

696
00:45:26,059 --> 00:45:29,570
In the US, you told Chan Yong about
me dating Kim Tan, didn't you?

697
00:45:29,570 --> 00:45:31,500
- So?
- How dare you say "So?"

698
00:45:31,699 --> 00:45:34,670
What right do you have to babble
about someone else's past?

699
00:45:34,670 --> 00:45:36,469
It's not like I made it up.
You should've...

700
00:45:36,469 --> 00:45:38,469
taken care of your boyfriend
in the first place.

701
00:45:38,539 --> 00:45:40,409
Why did you let him
flirt with another girl?

702
00:45:40,539 --> 00:45:44,480
I already took care of that issue
with Chan Young.

703
00:45:44,909 --> 00:45:47,320
I rather think there's something
between Tan and Eun Sang.

704
00:45:47,380 --> 00:45:48,619
Considering the circumstances.

705
00:45:48,619 --> 00:45:51,289
I have a lot of things that are
making me mad apart from you.

706
00:45:51,289 --> 00:45:53,360
I'm helping you accumulate
your anger more.

707
00:45:53,360 --> 00:45:55,320
I'll repay you
when everything is over.

708
00:45:57,489 --> 00:45:58,630
That's funny.

709
00:46:05,070 --> 00:46:06,340
Why did you come here in person?

710
00:46:06,699 --> 00:46:09,840
I had an appointment near here,
and I felt guilty to just leave.

711
00:46:09,840 --> 00:46:12,170
Your second marriage must not be
included in your guilt.

712
00:46:12,170 --> 00:46:14,010
Don't make me regret coming here.

713
00:46:17,179 --> 00:46:18,380
Isn't that Tan?

714
00:46:19,309 --> 00:46:20,480
Don't do that.

715
00:46:22,619 --> 00:46:23,889
That punk.

716
00:46:24,219 --> 00:46:26,619
He came back to Korea,
but never came by to say hello.

717
00:46:31,929 --> 00:46:33,659
It's been a long time, right?

718
00:46:33,829 --> 00:46:34,929
How have you been?

719
00:46:35,659 --> 00:46:39,599
You came back quite a while ago. You
should've visited me to say hello.

720
00:46:39,599 --> 00:46:41,369
I've been busy with several things.

721
00:46:41,369 --> 00:46:42,369
Is that so?

722
00:46:42,369 --> 00:46:43,869
We should still have
a meal together.

723
00:46:55,519 --> 00:46:57,389
That punk never says
something he doesn't mean.

724
00:46:58,389 --> 00:47:00,659
Well, that's better
than being embarrassed.

725
00:47:01,320 --> 00:47:02,889
Tan hit Young Do today.

726
00:47:02,960 --> 00:47:04,590
What? Why?

727
00:47:04,590 --> 00:47:07,159
Why? Because he did
something to deserve it.

728
00:47:07,800 --> 00:47:10,599
And I'm pretty sure Young Do
takes after his dad.

729
00:47:11,030 --> 00:47:14,369
One thing is clear. My fiance is
better than yours.

730
00:47:19,210 --> 00:47:20,909
Get out. I'm not going with you.

731
00:47:21,880 --> 00:47:23,710
Why did you come
in the first place then?

732
00:47:26,420 --> 00:47:28,519
Young Do hasn't arrived yet.

733
00:47:28,719 --> 00:47:30,750
Could you contact me when he comes?

734
00:47:30,750 --> 00:47:31,920
I'll be in the lounge.

735
00:47:32,019 --> 00:47:33,090
Okay.

736
00:47:33,420 --> 00:47:34,489
And Manager,

737
00:47:35,019 --> 00:47:37,429
CEO Kim Won of
Jeguk Group stays here, right?

738
00:47:37,659 --> 00:47:39,059
Yes, that's right.

739
00:47:39,059 --> 00:47:42,429
I come here often, but I think I've
been too indifferent to my in-laws.

740
00:47:43,099 --> 00:47:47,400
