of Jeguk Group's chief secretary?

741
00:47:47,400 --> 00:47:49,769
(Lee Esther)

742
00:47:55,139 --> 00:47:56,139
This is Yoon Jae Ho.

743
00:47:56,139 --> 00:47:58,579
