744
00:47:59,309 --> 00:48:01,719
I must be more desperate one
between the two of us.

745
00:48:02,449 --> 00:48:03,650
Do you think that's true?

746
00:48:04,349 --> 00:48:05,550
Don't act ambiguously.

747
00:48:06,050 --> 00:48:07,820
I got this number after
a lot of determination.

748
00:48:07,960 --> 00:48:11,030
I'm giving you a chance to think
more about whether it's worth it.

749
00:48:12,289 --> 00:48:13,360
I'll call you later.

750
00:48:13,559 --> 00:48:15,000
Are you going to hang up now?

751
00:48:16,500 --> 00:48:17,570
I'm going to hang up.

752
00:48:27,780 --> 00:48:28,780
Thank you.

753
00:48:32,010 --> 00:48:33,679
Are you dating these days?

754
00:48:35,119 --> 00:48:36,420
It's close to an affair.

755
00:48:36,420 --> 00:48:38,989
Even after watching me? Just stop.

756
00:48:39,820 --> 00:48:42,360
Okay, let's hear things
that will make my head hurt now.

757
00:48:43,559 --> 00:48:44,630
Report them to me.

758
00:48:45,860 --> 00:48:46,860
Yes.

759
00:48:48,559 --> 00:48:50,699
CEO Lee Esther of
RS International...

760
00:48:50,699 --> 00:48:53,800
currently owns 1.4 percent
of Jeguk Group's shares.

761
00:48:54,269 --> 00:48:56,269
