763
00:48:58,440 --> 00:49:00,710
when Tan and Rachel got engaged.

764
00:49:00,710 --> 00:49:03,110
She also owns
Hotel Zeus shares, right?

765
00:49:03,110 --> 00:49:04,110
Yes.

766
00:49:04,110 --> 00:49:06,179
She owns 1.1 percent,
so she already has a voting right...

767
00:49:06,179 --> 00:49:08,050
at the general shareholders meeting.

768
00:49:08,449 --> 00:49:11,050
After she marries Hotel Zeus
CEO Choi Dong Wook,

769
00:49:11,050 --> 00:49:13,190
she will own 3.4 percent
of Hotel Zeus shares...

770
