She will own 1.8 percent...

772
00:49:19,699 --> 00:49:21,960
Do you think this marriage
will really happen?

773
00:49:23,969 --> 00:49:26,269
Since it's not a love marriage,

774
00:49:27,599 --> 00:49:28,699
I think it will happen.

775
00:49:29,139 --> 00:49:30,170
Is that so?

776
00:49:58,699 --> 00:50:01,269
That's definitely
our company envelope. Who is he?

777
00:50:04,070 --> 00:50:05,940
We studied exactly up
to where I folded the page.

778
00:50:06,269 --> 00:50:08,409
This is the range where
the final exam will cover.

779
00:50:09,909 --> 00:50:11,650
It will also help you
if you study this.

780
00:50:12,550 --> 00:50:13,550
Thank you.

781
00:50:14,820 --> 00:50:16,849
(Don't Receive)

782
00:50:18,190 --> 00:50:19,920
What would I have done without you?

783
00:50:20,190 --> 00:50:21,260
Who is "Don't Receive"?

784
00:50:21,889 --> 00:50:23,760
I also have a secret, Friend.

785
00:50:24,190 --> 00:50:26,030
Hurry up and go.
Bo Na will lose her temper.

786
00:50:27,230 --> 00:50:29,929
Bo Na doesn't lose her temper.
She's just being cute.

787
00:50:29,929 --> 00:50:31,570
Gosh, you're a fool for her.

788
00:50:31,630 --> 00:50:32,630
I'll get going.

789
00:50:33,639 --> 00:50:35,500
- Call if you don't know something.
- Okay.

790
00:50:38,440 --> 00:50:40,179
(Don't Receive)

791
00:50:45,280 --> 00:50:47,320
- Why?
- I want to eat jjajangmyeon,

792
00:50:47,320 --> 00:50:49,079
but they won't deliver one dish.

793
00:50:49,079 --> 00:50:50,489
- What?
- Why don't you come here...

794
00:50:50,489 --> 00:50:51,719
and eat jjajangmyeon with me?

795
00:50:52,349 --> 00:50:54,920
Order two dishes and just eat one.
You're rich.

796
00:50:54,989 --> 00:50:57,530
How could you throw away food
when the economy is bad?

797
00:50:57,690 --> 00:50:59,860
Find someone else.
Why would I go there?

798
00:50:59,860 --> 00:51:01,030
You'll end up coming.

799
00:51:02,059 --> 00:51:03,570
Haven't you met Joon Young yet?

800
00:51:08,940 --> 00:51:10,010
I told him...

801
00:51:11,010 --> 00:51:12,670
that if he makes you come here,

802
00:51:13,380 --> 00:51:15,110
I might drop the charge.

803
00:51:16,309 --> 00:51:18,079
You punk! How could you...

804
00:51:20,150 --> 00:51:21,280
I'm going to hang up.

805
00:51:25,949 --> 00:51:26,960
Hey...

806
00:51:30,659 --> 00:51:31,690
I'm sorry, but...

807
00:51:34,760 --> 00:51:36,059
I'm really sorry, but...

808
00:51:45,239 --> 00:51:47,510
What is your intention
of playing with me?

809
00:51:56,750 --> 00:51:57,820
Intention?

810
00:51:57,820 --> 00:51:59,619
You're not even going to
really drop the charge.

811
00:51:59,619 --> 00:52:01,159
Why are you playing with people?

812
00:52:01,820 --> 00:52:04,059
Joon Young came to me looking like
he was about to die...

813
00:52:04,059 --> 00:52:05,059
to ask me a favor.

814
00:52:05,059 --> 00:52:06,960
You might be just playing,
but to him...

815
00:52:06,960 --> 00:52:08,230
Who said I was just playing?

816
00:52:09,829 --> 00:52:12,769
Are you really going to drop
the charge then?

817
00:52:12,769 --> 00:52:13,769
Yes.

818
00:52:14,269 --> 00:52:15,900
- Why?
- Because you came.

819
00:52:16,340 --> 00:52:17,809
What changes if I come?

820
00:52:17,809 --> 00:52:19,110
My mind will change.

821
00:52:19,110 --> 00:52:20,179
Why does it change?

822
00:52:20,179 --> 00:52:23,780
It's something like, "You became
a flower after coming to me."

823
00:52:24,949 --> 00:52:26,480
I'm not in the mood to joke.

824
00:52:26,480 --> 00:52:27,949
Do you think
everything I do is a joke?

825
00:52:31,320 --> 00:52:32,389
Don't you like flowers?

826
00:52:33,619 --> 00:52:35,619
Do you dislike the part "flower"
or "coming to me"?

827
00:52:35,619 --> 00:52:37,460
Pick one. I'll make you do
the part you dislike more.

828
00:52:38,530 --> 00:52:39,760
I dislike both.

829
00:52:40,559 --> 00:52:42,360
Gosh, I got dumped.

830
00:52:43,429 --> 00:52:44,630
I'm going to take revenge.

831
00:53:05,949 --> 00:53:07,190
Why aren't you answering my calls?

832
00:53:08,789 --> 00:53:10,690
I'm in the middle of a meal
with an important guest.

833
00:53:10,690 --> 00:53:12,159
You said you'd take care of it.

834
00:53:12,230 --> 00:53:14,300
But why are we taking
a photo on the weekend?

835
00:53:14,360 --> 00:53:15,900
I said I'm with a guest.

836
00:53:15,900 --> 00:53:16,900
A guest? Who?

837
00:53:25,909 --> 00:53:27,710
What kind of situation is this?

838
00:53:28,079 --> 00:53:31,250
Don't be curious.
I'm not going to let you join us.

839
00:53:31,650 --> 00:53:33,449
I also have no intention
to stay longer.

840
00:53:33,949 --> 00:53:35,949
Anyway, take care
of the photo thing properly.

841
00:53:36,050 --> 00:53:38,150
I'm not doing anything about it
because of you.

842
00:53:41,260 --> 00:53:43,489
You never cease to surprise me.

843
00:53:58,809 --> 00:54:00,139
Please drop the charge.

844
00:54:00,639 --> 00:54:02,480
I can go since
you're done eating, right?

845
00:54:02,710 --> 00:54:03,809
Where are you going?

846
00:54:04,449 --> 00:54:05,480
To work?

847
00:54:20,329 --> 00:54:21,329
It's me.

848
00:54:21,460 --> 00:54:23,469
Do you know where Chan Eun Sang is
and who she is with?

849
00:54:23,599 --> 00:54:25,699
- How would I know that?
- Do you want me to tell you?

850
00:54:25,800 --> 00:54:27,170
Didn't you call to tell me?

851
00:54:27,400 --> 00:54:29,739
Cha Eun Sang is in the suite
at Choi Young Do's hotel.

852
00:54:30,139 --> 00:54:31,969
She's eating with Choi Young Do
alone.

853
00:54:32,070 --> 00:54:33,210
I'm going to hang up.

854
00:54:44,619 --> 00:54:46,989
The person
you're calling cannot...

855
00:55:21,519 --> 00:55:23,889
Announcement for the
Jeguk High School parent meeting.

856
00:55:24,159 --> 00:55:27,630
There's a parent meeting
next Wednesday at 2pm.

857
00:55:30,599 --> 00:55:32,429
I'm Chan Eun Sang's mom.

858
00:55:32,699 --> 00:55:35,570
I'm sorry, but due to
unavoidable circumstances...

859
00:55:35,570 --> 00:55:36,809
What is it?

860
00:55:42,309 --> 00:55:45,250
Both you and I can't go
to our kid's school.

861
00:55:45,510 --> 00:55:46,780
Our lives are so sad.

862
00:55:50,250 --> 00:55:51,619
I'll be out for a moment.

863
00:55:51,920 --> 00:55:53,389
Where are you going at this hour?

864
00:56:17,380 --> 00:56:18,449
Come on out.

865
00:56:18,679 --> 00:56:20,179
Why? Did something happen?

866
00:56:23,420 --> 00:56:24,750
Why didn't you answer my calls?

867
00:56:25,119 --> 00:56:27,090
Can't you see that I'm working
right now?

868
00:56:27,090 --> 00:56:28,559
Did you go to Young Do's hotel?

869
00:56:29,559 --> 00:56:30,989
Gosh, Rachel.

870
00:56:31,059 --> 00:56:32,130
Did you go there?

871
00:56:32,929 --> 00:56:34,599
Does that hotel belong to
Young Do's family?

872
00:56:35,000 --> 00:56:36,059
Are you crazy?

873
00:56:36,769 --> 00:56:38,429
Why would you go there?

874
00:56:38,429 --> 00:56:40,400
I even went to your house
in the US...

875
00:56:40,400 --> 00:56:42,239
when you could've been
a drug dealer.

876
00:56:42,239 --> 00:56:44,610
I don't do stupid things.

877
00:56:44,610 --> 00:56:46,269
That's being stupid.

878
00:56:46,710 --> 00:56:48,679
How could you trust me
and follow me?

879
00:56:48,880 --> 00:56:50,309
Something bad could've happened.

880
00:56:51,079 --> 00:56:52,710
Because you'd never do
something to me.

881
00:56:52,750 --> 00:56:55,579
How do you know
whether I would or not?

882
00:56:58,849 --> 00:57:00,460
Why did you go to Young Do's hotel?

883
00:57:01,719 --> 00:57:02,889
Because of Joon Young.

884
00:57:03,559 --> 00:57:06,329
Choi Young Do said he would drop
the charge if I went there.

885
00:57:09,760 --> 00:57:12,530
- Did you believe that?
- I didn't, but what could I do...

886
00:57:12,530 --> 00:57:15,000
when a friend came to me and
desperately asked for a favor?

887
00:57:15,000 --> 00:57:16,940
How is he your friend?

888
00:57:17,340 --> 00:57:19,239
You've met him
just a couple of times.

889
00:57:19,239 --> 00:57:21,309
He knew that I am on
a welfare scholarship.

890
00:57:21,309 --> 00:57:22,940
He even knew what my mom does.

891
00:57:23,679 --> 00:57:25,949
But he still kept my secret.
How could I not go?

892
00:57:25,949 --> 00:57:27,980
He's going to transfer soon anyway.

893
00:57:28,679 --> 00:57:31,250
How many times did I tell you
not to be involved in such a thing?

894
00:57:33,760 --> 00:57:35,320
You want to pretend
to be nice that badly?

895
00:57:37,829 --> 00:57:40,030
Why is Choi Young Do
bullying me in the first place?

896
00:57:40,329 --> 00:57:41,329
It's because of you.

897
00:57:41,329 --> 00:57:42,599
That's why I'm like this.

898
00:57:43,030 --> 00:57:45,070
I'm afraid something might happen
to you because of me.

899
00:57:48,039 --> 00:57:49,300
I'm asking you.

900
00:57:50,340 --> 00:57:52,539
Can you please not do things
that will bother me?

901
00:57:53,440 --> 00:57:54,909
Can't you just stay low?

902
00:57:54,909 --> 00:57:56,949
Why don't you leave me alone?

903
00:57:58,449 --> 00:58:01,050
My life is already so hard as it is.

904
00:58:01,050 --> 00:58:03,079
But I got on Young Do's bad side
for some reason,

905
00:58:03,079 --> 00:58:04,650
and I'm getting more
uncomfortable with you.

906
00:58:05,949 --> 00:58:07,389
I'm not asking for something big.

907
00:58:07,659 --> 00:58:09,420
I just want to graduate safely...

908
00:58:09,420 --> 00:58:12,789
and live a better life when I'm 20,
even if it's just a little better.

909
00:58:14,059 --> 00:58:16,199
But I really don't know
what to do now.

910
00:58:18,730 --> 00:58:20,340
Should I tell you
what you should do?

911
00:58:22,670 --> 00:58:24,539
Get out of my house tomorrow.

912
00:58:27,139 --> 00:58:28,579
- What?
- You can't get out?

913
00:58:28,809 --> 00:58:30,480
Do you also want to continue
going to school?

914
00:58:31,050 --> 00:58:32,750
Then start liking me from now on.

915
00:58:32,949 --> 00:58:34,420
If possible, sincerely.

916
00:58:37,719 --> 00:58:39,050
I caught feelings for you.

917
00:59:12,820 --> 00:59:14,219
I said I like Cha Eun Sang.

918
00:59:14,219 --> 00:59:15,719
So? What do you want me to do
about it?

919
00:59:15,719 --> 00:59:16,719
Do we look good together?

920
00:59:16,719 --> 00:59:18,030
Why are you asking
such an ugly question?

921
00:59:18,030 --> 00:59:19,230
We look good together.

922
00:59:19,230 --> 00:59:21,030
If you behave like that,

923
00:59:21,030 --> 00:59:23,159
you and your mom can't stay
in this house.

924
00:59:23,159 --> 00:59:24,530
- Sit down.
- What is the meaning of...

925
00:59:24,530 --> 00:59:25,530
making me sit here?

926
00:59:25,530 --> 00:59:27,099
Stand up. I told you to stand up.

927
00:59:27,239 --> 00:59:28,840
What is wrong
with your table manners?

928
00:59:28,840 --> 00:59:30,000
You punk!

929
00:59:33,110 --> 00:59:39,980
(The Heirs)
